T232-无轨迹功能训练器 ​

设备类型代码（deviceType）设备类型设备名称
1T232无轨迹功能训练器

数据例子:

json
[
   {
    "ecc": 1,   
    "avgRfd": 105.65,
    "energy": 8.99,
    "maxRfd": 177.93,
    "indexId": 0,
    "maxLoad": 14.3,
    "avgPower": 42.82,
    "avgSpeed": 0.89,
    "maxPower": 73.1,
    "maxSpeed": 1.21,
    "direction": 1,
    "targetRfd": 0,
    "indexGroup": "0-1689209666204",
    "resistance": [
        11,
        11
    ],
    "targetLoad": 0,
    "targetPower": 0
    }
]

参数说明:

字段说明
ecc1 向心 2 离心
avgRfd平均Rfd
energy
maxRfd
indexId
maxLoad
avgPower
avgSpeed
maxPower
maxSpeed
direction
targetRfd
indexGroup
resistance
targetLoad
targetPower
